data.desc:
- Develop some APIs for NOBI applications using Laravel and Nodejs
- Migrate some of NOBI monolith API to a micro-services
- Migrate some of NOBI API from Laravel to Golang
- Develop NOBI internal application using Vue

- Develop Titik Pintar API that is being used in our mobile application, internal application, and other application.
- Develop Titik Pintar Admin Panel for our internal team.
- Develop Sahabat Pintar (https://sahabatpintar.id), both backend and frontend, for public use. That is a website for teachers, designers, and animators to contribute to our learning application
- Develop Titik Pintar Account Login. That is a website for parents to monitor their children's progress in our application
- Develop some features like multiplayer, live class, automation, and others for both our users and our internal team

- Develop web application for PT Wamplo Satu Interteknologi client using Laravel
- Develop mobile application for PT Wamplo Satu Interteknologi client using React Native

- Test application for ICON+ client
- Develop applications for ICON+ clients using Angular
